---
title: Warm Shrimp and Farro Salad with Green Beans, Sweet Bell Pepper, and Shallot-Lemon Citronette
description: Farro is an ideal base for any grain bowl—it’s not only nutritious, but nutty and delightfully chewy to boot! Tossed together with juicy shrimp, crispy-tender green beans, and caramelized bell pepper, this salad is one of our all-time favorites. Lemony shallot citronette is a great staple dressing to keep in your back pocket!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/570c098a4dab71175b8b4568.jpg
